---
import Layout from '@/layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="V-PACK Batarya Sistemi - Voltz Power Tools | Tek Platform, Sınırsız Güç"
  description="Voltz V-PACK batarya sistemi ile tek batarya, tüm aletler. 20V ve 16.8V seçenekleriyle 13+ ürünle uyumlu modüler batarya ekosistemi."
  keywords="v-pack batarya, modüler batarya sistemi, akülü alet bataryası, voltz batarya, 20V batarya, 16.8V batarya, power tools battery"
>

  <!-- Dark Hero with Stats -->
  <section class="vpack-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="vpack-hero-inner">
        <span class="section-tag">V-PACK EKOSİSTEMİ</span>
        <h1>V-PACK<br>BATARYA <span class="text-green">SİSTEMİ</span></h1>
        <p class="vpack-hero-desc">Tek batarya platformu, tüm Voltz aletleri. Geleceğin güç çözümü ile maksimum verimlilik ve maliyet tasarrufu.</p>
        <div class="hero-stats">
          <div class="hero-stat">
            <span class="hero-stat-value">20V</span>
            <span class="hero-stat-label">PROFESYONEL SERİ</span>
          </div>
          <div class="hero-stat-divider"></div>
          <div class="hero-stat">
            <span class="hero-stat-value">16.8V</span>
            <span class="hero-stat-label">KOMPAKT SERİ</span>
          </div>
          <div class="hero-stat-divider"></div>
          <div class="hero-stat">
            <span class="hero-stat-value">13+</span>
            <span class="hero-stat-label">UYUMLU ÜRÜN</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-diagonal"></div>
  </section>

  <!-- How It Works -->
  <section class="how-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="how-header">
        <span class="section-tag">NASIL ÇALIŞIR</span>
        <h2>ÜÇ ADIMDA <span class="text-green">BAŞLAYIN</span></h2>
        <p class="how-subtitle">V-PACK sistemi ile başlamak bu kadar kolay.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="how-grid">
        <div class="how-step">
          <div class="step-number">01</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <div class="step-icon">
              <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="1" y="6" width="22" height="12" rx="0" ry="0"/><line x1="23" y1="13" x2="23" y2="11"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3>BATARYANIZI SEÇİN</h3>
            <p>20V Profesyonel veya 16.8V Kompakt seriden ihtiyacınıza uygun bataryayı seçin.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="how-step">
          <div class="step-number">02</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <div class="step-icon">
              <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polygon points="13 2 3 14 12 14 11 22 21 10 12 10 13 2"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3>ŞARJ EDİN</h3>
            <p>Hızlı şarj cihazı ile kısa sürede tam güce ulaşın. Akıllı şarj koruması dahil.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="how-step">
          <div class="step-number">03</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <div class="step-icon">
              <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 0 0 1.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 0 1-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 0 1-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 0 1 7.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3>HERHANGİ BİR ALETLE KULLANIN</h3>
            <p>Aynı bataryayı tüm uyumlu Voltz aletlerinde takıp kullanın. Ekstra batarya gereksiz.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Platform Visual -->
  <section class="platform-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="platform-visual">
        <img src="/img/vpack-platform.png" alt="V-PACK Batarya Platformu - 20V ve 16.8V" class="platform-img" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Benefits Section -->
  <section class="benefits-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="benefits-header">
        <span class="section-tag">AVANTAJLAR</span>
        <h2>NEDEN <span class="text-green">V-PACK</span>?</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="benefits-grid">
        <div class="benefit-card">
          <div class="benefit-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="12" y1="1" x2="12" y2="23"/><path d="M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>MALİYET TASARRUFU</h3>
          <p>Tek batarya ile tüm aletlerinizi çalıştırarak batarya maliyetlerini %70'e kadar azaltın.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="benefit-card">
          <div class="benefit-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>KOLAY KULLANIM</h3>
          <p>Aletler arası batarya geçişi saniyeler içinde. Tek tık ile tak-çıkar mekanizması.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="benefit-card">
          <div class="benefit-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="1" y="6" width="22" height="12" rx="0" ry="0"/><line x1="23" y1="13" x2="23" y2="11"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>UZUN ÖMÜR</h3>
          <p>5000+ şarj döngüsü garantili Li-ion hücreler. Akıllı BMS ile aşırı şarj/deşarj koruması.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="benefit-card">
          <div class="benefit-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polygon points="12 2 2 7 12 12 22 7 12 2"/><polyline points="2 17 12 22 22 17"/><polyline points="2 12 12 17 22 12"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>GENİŞ ÜRÜN YELPAZESİ</h3>
          <p>13'ten fazla ürünle uyumlu ve sürekli büyüyen ekosistem. Yeni ürünler otomatik uyumlu.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-card">
        <div class="cta-inner">
          <span class="section-tag section-tag--dark">V-PACK EKOSİSTEMİ</span>
          <h2>V-PACK EKOSİSTEMİNE GEÇİN</h2>
          <p>Profesyonel iş akışınızı sadeleştirin, maliyetlerinizi düşürün. Voltz V-PACK ile gücü keşfedin.</p>
          <div class="cta-buttons">
            <a href="/products" class="btn-angular btn-angular--green">
              ÜRÜNLERİ KEŞFET
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 8h10M9 4l4 4-4 4"/></svg>
            </a>
            <a href="/contact" class="btn-outline">İLETİŞİME GEÇİN</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer class="site-footer">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="footer-grid">
        <div class="footer-brand"><img src="/img/logo/voltz-symbol-green.png" alt="Voltz" class="footer-logo"><p>Profesyonel el aletlerinde güvenin adresi.</p></div>
        <div class="footer-links"><h4>Sayfalar</h4><a href="/">Anasayfa</a><a href="/about">Hakkımızda</a><a href="/products">Ürünlerimiz</a><a href="/contact">İletişim</a></div>
        <div class="footer-links"><h4>Ürünler</h4><a href="/products">Matkaplar</a><a href="/products">Tornavidalar</a><a href="/products">Taşlama</a><a href="/v-pack">V-PACK</a></div>
        <div class="footer-contact-col"><h4>İletişim</h4><p>Teknoloji Caddesi No: 123<br>Sanayi Mahallesi, İstanbul</p><a href="mailto:info@voltzpowertools.com">info@voltzpowertools.com</a><a href="tel:+902123456789">+90 212 345 67 89</a></div>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-bottom"><p>&copy; 2025 Voltz Power Tools.</p><div class="footer-social"><a href="#">LI</a><a href="#">IG</a></div></div>
    </div>
  </footer>

</Layout>

<style>
  .text-green { color: var(--green); }

  .section-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 6px 16px;
    background: rgba(107, 224, 63, 0.1);
    color: var(--green);
    font-family: 'GeneralSans-Bold', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(107, 224, 63, 0.2);
  }

  .section-tag--dark {
    background: rgba(107, 224, 63, 0.15);
    border-color: rgba(107, 224, 63, 0.3);
  }

  /* ========== HERO ========== */
  .vpack-hero {
    padding: 100px 0 140px;
    background: var(--darker, #111);
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .vpack-hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    background: repeating-linear-gradient(
      90deg,
      transparent,
      transparent 80px,
      rgba(255,255,255,0.02) 80px,
      rgba(255,255,255,0.02) 81px
    );
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .hero-diagonal {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 60px;
    background: var(--white, #fff);
    clip-path: polygon(0 100%, 100% 0, 100% 100%);
  }

  .vpack-hero-inner {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .vpack-hero .section-tag {
    background: rgba(107, 224, 63, 0.15);
    border-color: rgba(107, 224, 63, 0.3);
  }

  .vpack-hero h1 {
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .vpack-hero-desc {
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    max-width: 560px;
    margin: 0 auto 48px;
  }

  .hero-stats {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 40px;
    padding: 32px 56px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  }

  .hero-stat {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 6px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .hero-stat-value {
    font-family: 'GeneralSans-Bold', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 36px;
    color: var(--green);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .hero-stat-label {
    font-family: 'GeneralSans-Bold', sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .hero-stat-divider {
    width: 1px;
    height: 48px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  }

  /* ========== HOW IT WORKS ========== */
  .how-section {
    padding: 100px 0;
    background: var(--white);
  }

  .how-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 64px;
  }

  .how-header h2 {
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .how-subtitle {
    font-size: 17px;
    color: var(--gray-500);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .how-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 32px;
  }

  .how-step {
    padding: 40px 28px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: var(--white);
  }

  .how-step::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 3px;
    background: var(--green);
    transform: scaleX(0);
    transform-origin: left;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .how-step:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    border-color: var(--green);
  }

  .how-step:hover::before {
    transform: scaleX(1);
  }

  .step-number {
    font-family: 'GeneralSans-Bold', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 56px;
    color: rgba(107, 224, 63, 0.12);
    position: absolute;
    top: 12px;
    right: 20px;
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: -2px;
  }

  .step-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .step-icon {
    width: 56px;
    height: 56px;
    background: rgba(107, 224, 63, 0.1);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: var(--green);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .how-step h3 {
    font-size: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }

  .how-step p {
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--gray-500);
  }

  /* ========== PLATFORM VISUAL ========== */
  .platform-section {
    padding: 80px 0;
    background: var(--white);
  }

  .platform-visual {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .platform-img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
  }

  /* ========== BENEFITS ========== */
  .benefits-section {
    padding: 100px 0;
    background: var(--gray-100);
  }

  .benefits-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 64px;
  }

  .benefits-header h2 {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .benefits-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .benefit-card {
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 36px 28px;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
    position: relative;
  }

  .benefit-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 4px;
    height: 0;
    background: var(--green);
    transition: height 0.3s ease;
  }

  .benefit-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    border-color: var(--green);
  }

  .benefit-card:hover::before {
    height: 100%;
  }

  .benefit-icon {
    width: 52px;
    height: 52px;
    background: rgba(107, 224, 63, 0.1);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: var(--green);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .benefit-card h3 {
    font-size: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }

  .benefit-card p {
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--gray-500);
  }

  /* ========== CTA ========== */
  .cta-section {
    padding: 0 0 100px;
    background: var(--gray-100);
  }

  .cta-card {
    background: var(--dark);
    padding: 80px 48px;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .cta-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    background: repeating-linear-gradient(
      90deg,
      transparent,
      transparent 100px,
      rgba(255,255,255,0.015) 100px,
      rgba(255,255,255,0.015) 101px
    );
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .cta-inner {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .cta-card h2 {
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .cta-card p {
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    margin-bottom: 36px;
  }

  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .btn-angular {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    padding: 16px 36px;
    background: var(--dark);
    color: var(--white);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-family: 'GeneralSans-Bold', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 14px;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 100% calc(100% - 8px), calc(100% - 8px) 100%, 0 100%);
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .btn-angular--green {
    background: var(--green);
    color: var(--dark);
  }

  .btn-angular--green:hover {
    background: var(--green-dark);
  }

  .btn-angular svg {
    transition: transform 0.2s ease;
  }

  .btn-angular:hover svg {
    transform: translateX(3px);
  }

  .btn-outline {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 16px 36px;
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--white);
    border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-family: 'GeneralSans-Bold', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 14px;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .btn-outline:hover {
    border-color: var(--white);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
  }

  /* ========== FOOTER ========== */
  .site-footer { background: var(--darker, #111); padding: 64px 0 32px; color: #fff; }
  .footer-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr 1.5fr; gap: 48px; padding-bottom: 48px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); }
  .footer-logo { height: 48px; width: auto; display: block; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .footer-brand p { font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); }
  .footer-links h4, .footer-contact-col h4 { font-family: 'GeneralSans-Bold', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; color: var(--green, #6BE03F); margin-bottom: 16px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .footer-links a, .footer-contact-col a { display: block; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); text-decoration: none; font-size: 14px; padding: 4px 0; transition: color 0.2s; }
  .footer-links a:hover, .footer-contact-col a:hover { color: var(--green, #6BE03F); }
  .footer-contact-col p { font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .footer-bottom { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; padding-top: 24px; }
  .footer-bottom p { font-size: 13px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3); }
  .footer-social { display: flex; gap: 8px; }
  .footer-social a { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; width: 36px; height: 36px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s; }
  .footer-social a:hover { background: var(--green, #6BE03F); color: var(--dark, #1A1A1A); }

  /* ========== RESPONSIVE ========== */
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .benefits-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
    .hero-stats { gap: 32px; padding: 28px 40px; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .vpack-hero { padding: 64px 0 120px; }
    .vpack-hero-desc { font-size: 16px; }
    .hero-stats { flex-direction: column; gap: 24px; padding: 28px 24px; }
    .hero-stat-divider { width: 48px; height: 1px; }
    .hero-stat-value { font-size: 28px; }
    .how-section, .benefits-section { padding: 64px 0; }
    .how-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 20px; }
    .how-step { display: flex; gap: 0; text-align: left; padding: 24px; }
    .step-number { display: none; }
    .benefits-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 16px; }
    .benefit-card { display: flex; gap: 20px; align-items: flex-start; padding: 24px; }
    .benefit-icon { flex-shrink: 0; margin-bottom: 0; }
    .cta-section { padding: 0 0 64px; }
    .cta-card { padding: 48px 24px; }
    .cta-buttons { flex-direction: column; align-items: stretch; }
    .btn-angular, .btn-outline { justify-content: center; text-align: center; }
    .footer-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; text-align: center; gap: 32px; }
    .footer-bottom { flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; text-align: center; }
    .footer-social { justify-content: center; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .hero-stats { padding: 24px 16px; gap: 20px; }
  }
</style>
